{
    title: "Один подрядчик",
    description: "Полный цикл: замер, производство, монтаж.",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 18l-4-4-4 4"/><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 13h6"/></svg>`
  },
  {
