    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18M8 14h.01M12 14h.01M16 14h.01M8 18h.01M12 18h.01"/></svg>`
    title: "Строители с опытом более 7 лет",
    description: "Опытные специалисты, которые отвечают за качество.",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18M8 14h.01M12 14h.01M16 14h.01M8 18h.01M12 18h.01"/></svg>`
